headline: TD SYNNEX Is Named NetApp North America Distributor of the Year for FY’25
summary: FREMONT, Calif. & CLEARWATER, Fla., August 13, 2025--TD SYNNEX today announced it has been named NetApp’s North America Distributor of the Year for FY’25.

headline: NetApp Recognizes Winners of 2025 North America Partner Awards
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., August 13, 2025--NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today announced the winners of its North America Partner Awards for Fiscal Year 2025 (FY’25). NetApp’s strategic partnerships aid in providing NetApp products and solutions to solve the business challenges of their joint customers.
